### 1. [high] `fathomdb-py` no-feature builds are broken by an unguarded CLS helper
Refs: [lib.rs:1678](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-py/src/lib.rs:1678), [lib.rs:95](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-embedder/src/lib.rs:95), [Cargo.toml:15](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-py/Cargo.toml:15)

`cls_embedder_singleton()` is compiled unconditionally, but it directly references `fathomdb_embedder::CandleBgeEmbedder` and `Pooling`, which only exist when `fathomdb-embedder/default-embedder` is enabled. `fathomdb-py` still declares `default = []` and keeps `default-embedder` opt-in. That means the preserved no-feature Python build path should stop compiling, which is a direct opt-in-discipline regression.

### 2. [medium] `embed_batch_cls` permanently poisons itself on first load failure and misreports the cause
Refs: [lib.rs:1678](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-py/src/lib.rs:1678), [lib.rs:1709](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-py/src/lib.rs:1709), [lib.rs:1725](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-py/src/lib.rs:1725)

The singleton caches `Option<CandleBgeEmbedder>` in a `OnceLock` and uses `.ok()`, so any transient loader failure becomes cached `None` for the life of the process. After that, every failure is flattened to `EmbedderNotConfiguredError("cache miss + no network")`, even for checksum, deserialize, permission, or other loader errors. The panic boundary is fine, but the error handling is not sane.

### 3. [medium] The new public Python symbol is exported at runtime but missing from the stub surface
Refs: [__init__.py:15](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/python/fathomdb/__init__.py:15), [__init__.py:59](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/python/fathomdb/__init__.py:59), [_fathomdb.pyi:287](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/python/fathomdb/_fathomdb.pyi:287), [_fathomdb.pyi:313](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb-worktrees/0.8.14-slice-25-20260704T033943Z/src/python/fathomdb/_fathomdb.pyi:313)

